sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant Main as MainDashboard
  participant NAV as NavigationContainer
  participant DPS as DynamicProximitySearch
  participant Socket as SocketServer
  participant HelperDash as HelperDashboard
  participant HelperNotif as HelperSOSNotification
  participant HelperTrack as HelperTracking
  participant Directions as DirectionsAPI
  participant Phone as Phone

  User->>Main: pressSOS()  (onPress handler in `MainDashboard`)
  Main->>NAV: navigation.navigate('EmergencySearch')
  NAV->>DPS: render `DynamicProximitySearch` (route: EmergencySearch)
  DPS->>DPS: setState(radiusInMeters=250)
  DPS->>Socket: (conceptual) emit 'sos_alert' to server

  alt server expands search
    Socket-->>DPS: 'search_expanded' (payload: { radius: 1000 })
    DPS->>DPS: setRadiusInMeters(1000); animateToRegion(...)
  end

  alt escalation reached
    Socket-->>DPS: 'max_radius_reached'
    DPS->>Phone: Linking.openURL('tel:911')  -- opens dialer to call 911
  end

  Note right of Socket: Server notifies helpers via socket
  Socket-->>HelperDash: 'incoming_sos' (victim params)
  HelperDash->>HelperNotif: navigation.navigate('HelperSOSNotification', params)

  HelperNotif->>HelperTrack: navigation.replace('HelperTracking', params)
  HelperTrack->>Directions: fetchRoute(HELPER_START, victimLocation, GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY)
  Directions-->>HelperTrack: { coordinates, distanceText, durationText } (or null)
  HelperTrack->>HelperTrack: simulate movement along route (setHelperLocation)

  alt helper arrives
    HelperTrack->>NAV: navigation.replace('SOSCompletion', { victimName, responseTime, distanceCovered, outcome })
    NAV->>SOSComplete: render `SOSCompletion` screen
    SOSComplete->>NAV: navigation.reset([{ AuthScreen }, { MainDashboard }, { HelperDashboard }])
  end

  Note left of Main: Auth flow uses navigation.replace('MainDashboard') after sign-in
